Class CefXmlReader

CefBase
   |
   +--CefXmlReader
   in cef_xml_reader.h
class CefXmlReader
extends CefBase

Class that supports the reading of XML data via the libxml streaming API. The methods of this class should only be called on the thread that creates the object.
